      • waitForCopyResult

        public CopyResult waitForCopyResult()
                             throws CosClientException,
                                    CosServiceException,
                                    InterruptedException
        Waits for this copy operation to complete and returns the result of the operation. Be prepared to handle errors when calling this method. Any errors that occurred during the asynchronous transfer will be re-thrown through this method.
        Specified by:
        waitForCopyResult in interface Copy
        Returns:
        The result of this transfer.
        Throws:
        CosClientException - If any errors are encountered in the client while making the request or handling the response.
        CosServiceException - If any errors occurred in COS while processing the request.
        InterruptedException - If this thread is interrupted while waiting for the upload to complete.
